<font face="Serif" size="18">It's kind of funky
to breathe under here.</font>

363
00:21:11,687 --> 00:21:14,315
<font face="Serif" size="18">Drac. Hey, Drac.
How'd it go with Mavey?</font>

364
00:21:14,398 --> 00:21:16,696
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey. Where'd you go?</font>

365
00:21:19,195 --> 00:21:20,287
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wow!</font>

366
00:21:20,362 --> 00:21:22,285
<font face="Serif" size="18">This room's kind of
small for a big castle.</font>

367
00:21:22,364 --> 00:21:25,243
<font face="Serif" size="18">No bed, but check out these
awesome dustpans they give you.</font>

368
00:21:25,367 --> 00:21:26,744
<font face="Serif" size="18">Quiet, you fool.</font>

369
00:21:26,827 --> 00:21:29,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">What weapons are you keeping
in this container?</font>

370
00:21:29,079 --> 00:21:30,672
<font face="Serif" size="18">Your pitchforks?</font>

371
00:21:31,248 --> 00:21:32,340
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh!</font>

372
00:21:32,416 --> 00:21:33,918
<font face="Serif" size="18">I can't breathe.</font>

373
00:21:34,001 --> 00:21:35,503
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's killing me.</font>

374
00:21:35,586 --> 00:21:38,135
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, definitely due
for a fluff and fold.</font>

375
00:21:38,214 --> 00:21:39,575
<font face="Serif" size="18">What is this?</font>

376
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:40,807
<font face="Serif" size="18">A torture device?</font>

377
00:21:40,883 --> 00:21:42,556
<font face="Serif" size="18">A secret mind controller?</font>

378
00:21:42,635 --> 00:21:44,478
<font face="Serif" size="18">You won't read my thoughts.</font>

379
00:21:44,553 --> 00:21:45,770
<font face="Serif" size="18">I won't let you.</font>

380
00:21:45,846 --> 00:21:47,439
<font face="Serif" size="18">Dude, it's just music.</font>

381
00:21:47,515 --> 00:21:48,812
<font face="Serif" size="18">Here, try it.</font>

382
00:21:50,559 --> 00:21:51,811
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ohh!</font>

383
00:21:51,894 --> 00:21:54,773
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's taking my soul!</font>

384
00:21:55,731 --> 00:21:58,905
<font face="Serif" size="18">What? It's a good jam.
Don't be a grandpa.</font>

385
00:21:58,984 --> 00:22:00,486
<font face="Serif" size="18">You need to go.</font>

386
00:22:00,569 --> 00:22:05,450
<font face="Serif" size="18">No human has ever entered this castle.
And if someone should see you,</font>

387
00:22:05,533 --> 00:22:11,506
<font face="Serif" size="18">the safety of the hotel, the sanctuary,
no one would ever come again.</font>

388
00:22:11,580 --> 00:22:13,548
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, go for it.</font>

389
00:22:13,624 --> 00:22:15,592
<font face="Serif" size="18">"Ever come again!"</font>

390
00:22:15,668 --> 00:22:19,047
<font face="Serif" size="18">I love your Dracula voice.
It's so over the top.</font>

391
00:22:19,129 --> 00:22:23,760
<font face="Serif" size="18">And Mavis, if she saw you, she
would know that I lied. No!</font>

392
00:22:23,843 --> 00:22:25,720
<font face="Serif" size="18">Who's Mavis?
Is this her room?</font>

393
00:22:25,803 --> 00:22:26,895
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm good with a roommate.</font>

394
00:22:26,971 --> 00:22:29,132
<font face="Serif" size="18">I had six brothers growing
up, sol could totally share.</font>

395
00:22:29,139 --> 00:22:30,265
<font face="Serif" size="18">I can't kill him.</font>

396
00:22:30,349 --> 00:22:32,522
<font face="Serif" size="18">It would set monsters back
hundreds of years.</font>

397
00:22:32,601 --> 00:22:34,274
<font face="Serif" size="18">One time, in Hamburg,
I roomed with this dude</font>

398
00:22:34,353 --> 00:22:35,855
<font face="Serif" size="18">who I caught stealing
my shampoo.</font>

399
00:22:35,938 --> 00:22:39,192
<font face="Serif" size="18">I said, "Whoa, man," and he threw a
flower pot at me, but he was cool.</font>

400
00:22:39,275 --> 00:22:40,652
<font face="Serif" size="18">What are you babbling about?</font>

401
00:22:40,734 --> 00:22:42,236
<font face="Serif" size="18">What? Whoa.</font>

402
00:22:42,319 --> 00:22:44,037
<font face="Serif" size="18">Check out these
awesome costumes.</font>

403
00:22:44,113 --> 00:22:45,706
<font face="Serif" size="18">Costumes.</font>

404
00:22:46,574 --> 00:22:49,544
<font face="Serif" size="18">What's this? Sorry, man. I just
can't be without my backpack.</font>

405
00:22:49,660 --> 00:22:52,163
<font face="Serif" size="18">You know, everything I own's in there.
It'll be right here.</font>

406
00:22:52,246 --> 00:22:54,840
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, I just...
I love my backpack.</font>

407
00:22:54,915 --> 00:22:56,417
<font face="Serif" size="18">Whoa. Hey, what are you doing?</font>

408
00:22:56,500 --> 00:22:58,502
<font face="Serif" size="18">What are you... What are
you doing to my hair?</font>

409
00:22:58,586 --> 00:23:01,055
<font face="Serif" size="18">Stop. Oh, wait, that tickles.</font>

410
00:23:01,130 --> 00:23:03,349
<font face="Serif" size="18">Come on, man.</font>

411
00:23:06,969 --> 00:23:09,017
<font face="Serif" size="18">Check it out.
I'm a Franken-homie.</font>

412
00:23:09,096 --> 00:23:10,894
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yes, hello.
Look at me!</font>

413
00:23:10,973 --> 00:23:14,978
<font face="Serif" size="18">This is totally normal, not a problem here.
This is just a monster with me.</font>

414
00:23:15,102 --> 00:23:16,695
<font face="Serif" size="18">Man, everybody
stepped it up tonight.</font>

415
00:23:17,479 --> 00:23:20,528
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait, why are we going to the front door?
Are we leaving?</font>

416
00:23:20,608 --> 00:23:22,702
<font face="Serif" size="18">Bonjour, Dracula!</font>

417
00:23:22,776 --> 00:23:24,528
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, Sniffy.
What's going on?</font>

418
00:23:24,612 --> 00:23:26,455
<font face="Serif" size="18">Not right now, Quasimodo.</font>

419
00:23:28,949 --> 00:23:30,075
<font face="Serif" size="18">What?</font>

420
00:23:30,159 --> 00:23:32,207
<font face="Serif" size="18">No. Don't be absurd.</font>

421
00:23:32,286 --> 00:23:35,085
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's not a human,
but Monsieur Dracula.</font>

422
00:23:35,205 --> 00:23:37,207
<font face="Serif" size="18">How ridiculous. It's me.</font>

423
00:23:39,585 --> 00:23:40,632
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">Monsieur.</font></font></i></font>

424
00:23:40,753 --> 00:23:43,347
<font face="Serif" size="18">The devilled lizard fingers.
Devilled lizard fingers?</font>

425
00:23:43,422 --> 00:23:45,140
<font face="Serif" size="18">I asked for
spleens-in-blankets.</font>

426
00:23:45,215 --> 00:23:47,263
<font face="Serif" size="18">You ugly fool! I told
you, he doesn't like</font>

427
00:23:47,343 --> 00:23:48,845
<font face="Serif" size="18">the lizard fingers!
But you said...</font>

428
00:23:50,804 --> 00:23:53,227
<font face="Serif" size="18">Whoa. Check that costume out.</font>

429
00:23:53,307 --> 00:23:57,653
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wow. Seriously, I just have to ask
you: How are you pulling this off?</font>

430
00:23:57,728 --> 00:23:59,230
<font face="Serif" size="18">I mean, it looks so real.</font>

431
00:23:59,313 --> 00:24:01,566
<font face="Serif" size="18">Like, I could just put
my hand right through...</font>

432
00:24:03,442 --> 00:24:04,682
<font face="Serif" size="18">What do you think you're doing?</font>

433
00:24:04,693 --> 00:24:07,788
<font face="Serif" size="18">She's real. You're real!</font>

434
00:24:07,863 --> 00:24:11,618
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, and I'll give you a real beating.
Keep your hands out of my wife!</font>

435
00:24:15,913 --> 00:24:17,165
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, no.</font>

436
00:24:19,208 --> 00:24:20,255
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ay-yi-yi-yi!</font>

437
00:24:55,869 --> 00:24:57,542
<font face="Serif" size="18">Honey, I just didn't
know where you were.</font>

438
00:24:57,621 --> 00:24:59,623
<font face="Serif" size="18">We thought you were still out.</font>

439
00:24:59,707 --> 00:25:02,301
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, no. I don't know why
I ever wanted to leave.</font>

440
00:25:02,376 --> 00:25:04,299
<font face="Serif" size="18">The humans are so boring.</font>

441
00:25:17,558 --> 00:25:19,560
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mavis, honey,
are you all right?</font>

442
00:25:19,643 --> 00:25:22,738
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, I think so.
That was weird.</font>

443
00:25:22,813 --> 00:25:24,736
<font face="Serif" size="18">My head hurts.</font>

444
00:25:24,815 --> 00:25:26,738
<font face="Serif" size="18">Um, who is that?
Who is what?</font>

445
00:25:26,817 --> 00:25:28,410
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, that.</font>

446
00:25:28,485 --> 00:25:30,408
<font face="Serif" size="18">That is nobody.</font>

447
00:25:30,487 --> 00:25:32,285
<font face="Serif" size="18">Seriously, Dad?
"Dad"?</font>

448
00:25:32,364 --> 00:25:36,164
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, I know, Dracula's daughter.
Everyone freaks out at first.</font>

449
00:25:36,243 --> 00:25:37,415
<font face="Serif" size="18">Dracula?</font>

450
00:25:37,494 --> 00:25:38,586
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, we got to go.</font>

451
00:25:42,374 --> 00:25:44,251
<font face="Serif" size="18">Please don't kill me.
I'm so young.</font>

452
00:25:44,334 --> 00:25:46,678
<font face="Serif" size="18">I have so many
places I want to see.</font>

453
00:25:46,754 --> 00:25:49,007
<font face="Serif" size="18">I've got tickets to six
Dave Matthews Band concerts.</font>

454
00:25:49,089 --> 00:25:50,966
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm getting out of here.</font>

455
00:25:54,261 --> 00:25:55,638
<font face="Serif" size="18">Shut up already.</font>

456
00:25:55,721 --> 00:25:58,270
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's impossible for me
to think with all your noise.</font>

457
00:25:58,348 --> 00:26:00,567
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sorry, Glen.
Go back to sleep.</font>

458
00:26:02,436 --> 00:26:06,782
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait. Aren't you going to suck my blood?
Classic human paranoia.</font>

459
00:26:06,857 --> 00:26:10,828
<font face="Serif" size="18">Human blood is so fatty, and you
never know where it's been.</font>

460
00:26:10,903 --> 00:26:13,656
<font face="Serif" size="18">So, Dracula doesn't
drink blood?</font>

461
00:26:13,739 --> 00:26:16,162
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, I use a blood substitute.</font>

462
00:26:16,241 --> 00:26:20,542
<font face="Serif" size="18">Either Near Blood or Blood Beaters.
You can't tell the difference.</font>

463
00:26:20,621 --> 00:26:23,465
<font face="Serif" size="18">So, wow, you're, like,
the real Count Dracula.</font>

464
00:26:23,540 --> 00:26:26,293
<font face="Serif" size="18">Like, "I'm Dracula.
Bleh, bleh-bleh."</font>

465
00:26:26,376 --> 00:26:30,006
<font face="Serif" size="18">I've never said that in my life.
"Bleh, bleh-bleh."</font>

466
00:26:30,089 --> 00:26:31,807
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't know where
that comes from.</font>

467
00:26:31,882 --> 00:26:35,307
<font face="Serif" size="18">Can I just ask, what
exactly is this place?</font>

468
00:26:35,385 --> 00:26:37,808
<font face="Serif" size="18">What is this place?</font>

469
00:26:41,683 --> 00:26:45,733
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's a place I built for all
those monsters out there,</font>

470
00:26:45,813 --> 00:26:51,161
<font face="Serif" size="18">lurking in the shadows, hiding
from the persecution of humankind.</font>

471
00:26:51,360 --> 00:26:55,740
<font face="Serif" size="18">A place for them and their families
to come to and be themselves.</font>

472
00:26:55,864 --> 00:26:59,243
<font face="Serif" size="18">A place void of torches,
pitchforks, angry mobs.</font>

473
00:26:59,368 --> 00:27:02,588
<font face="Serif" size="18">A place of peace, relaxation</font>

474
00:27:02,704 --> 00:27:04,923
<font face="Serif" size="18">and tranquility.</font>

475
00:27:05,040 --> 00:27:07,088
<font face="Serif" size="18">Cool. So, it's like
a hotel for monsters?</font>

476
00:27:08,127 --> 00:27:12,052
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yes, exactly. "A hotel for
monsters." Way to sum it up.</font>

477
00:27:13,257 --> 00:27:16,557
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, hop on my back.
We're leaving.</font>

478
00:27:16,635 --> 00:27:18,262
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, man, you're a bat now.</font>

479
00:27:18,387 --> 00:27:20,230
<font face="Serif" size="18">I always wanted to fly.
What's it like?</font>

480
00:27:20,806 --> 00:27:23,434
<font face="Serif" size="18">This is insane. Wait.
Wait, I want to stay.</font>

481
00:27:23,559 --> 00:27:26,062
<font face="Serif" size="18">Can Frankenstein sign my costume?
Can I meet the Invisible Man?</font>

482
00:27:26,145 --> 00:27:28,614
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, if I stuck my hand
in the Invisible Man's mouth,</font>

483
00:27:28,730 --> 00:27:30,277
<font face="Serif" size="18">- would it disappear?
- Hi.</font>

484
00:27:30,399 --> 00:27:34,245
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mavey! What are you doing,
my sweet little blood orange?</font>

485
00:27:34,319 --> 00:27:36,367
<font face="Serif" size="18">Our friend was just leaving.</font>

486
00:27:36,446 --> 00:27:38,414
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, he was flying
me out the window.</font>

487
00:27:39,658 --> 00:27:41,035
<font face="Serif" size="18">This guy, he's so funny.</font>

488
00:27:41,118 --> 00:27:43,587
<font face="Serif" size="18">Look, you have
something on your face.</font>

489
00:27:43,662 --> 00:27:47,417
<font face="Serif" size="18">Play along if you ever want
to see your precious backpack.</font>

490
00:27:50,169 --> 00:27:54,049
<font face="Serif" size="18">Whoa. So, wait, you didn't have any
clothes on when you were a bat?</font>

491
00:27:54,131 --> 00:27:55,428
<font face="Serif" size="18">Or were they bat-sized?</font>

492
00:27:55,507 --> 00:27:57,635
<font face="Serif" size="18">Who exactly is that?</font>

493
00:27:58,635 --> 00:27:59,978
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hmm. Honeybat.</font>

494
00:28:00,095 --> 00:28:02,268
<font face="Serif" size="18">You see, it's your birthday.</font>

495
00:28:02,347 --> 00:28:07,148
<font face="Serif" size="18">And you know I want you to have the
bestest, specialest party of your life.</font>

496
00:28:07,269 --> 00:28:10,523
<font face="Serif" size="18">So, well, I needed some help.</font>

497
00:28:10,606 --> 00:28:11,823
<font face="Serif" size="18">You needed help?</font>

498
00:28:11,940 --> 00:28:15,319
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, look, I am very good,
but I thought it would be</font>

499
00:28:15,444 --> 00:28:20,792
<font face="Serif" size="18">even more bestest, specialest if someone
closer to your age helped plan the party.</font>

500
00:28:20,866 --> 00:28:22,118
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're my age?
Sure.</font>

501
00:28:22,201 --> 00:28:23,828
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, how old are you?</font>

502
00:28:23,952 --> 00:28:24,999
<font face="Serif" size="18">118.</font>

503
00:28:25,120 --> 00:28:26,872
<font face="Serif" size="18">One hundred and...</font>

504
00:28:26,955 --> 00:28:29,754
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, I'm 121.</font>

505
00:28:29,833 --> 00:28:31,631
<font face="Serif" size="18">Really?
Mm-hmm.</font>

506
00:28:31,710 --> 00:28:35,465
<font face="Serif" size="18">You see? Everything
is very, very normal.</font>

507
00:28:35,547 --> 00:28:38,300
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm throwing a party,
and he's helping.</font>

508
00:28:38,383 --> 00:28:40,681
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sir, there's an emergency.
Not now.</font>

509
00:28:40,802 --> 00:28:44,352
<font face="Serif" size="18">Can't you see we're in the middle
of something very normal here?</font>

510
00:28:44,473 --> 00:28:45,975
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait, what's going on here?</font>

511
00:28:46,058 --> 00:28:50,313
<font face="Serif" size="18">There's an emergency in your precious
hotel, and you're not running to fix it?</font>

512
00:28:50,479 --> 00:28:51,981
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why? Is it because of him?</font>

513
00:28:52,064 --> 00:28:53,907
<font face="Serif" size="18">Whoa, look at my face.</font>

514
00:28:54,775 --> 00:28:57,995
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, precious bones,
it's not because of him.</font>

515
00:28:58,070 --> 00:29:00,914
<font face="Serif" size="18">Good. Then go check on the emergency,
and I'll keep him company.</font>

516
00:29:00,989 --> 00:29:03,913
<font face="Serif" size="18">No! Anything but that!
What?</font>

517
00:29:03,992 --> 00:29:06,711
<font face="Serif" size="18">I mean, because
he needs time to plan.</font>

518
00:29:06,787 --> 00:29:09,666
<font face="Serif" size="18">And if you're keeping him
company, then he's not planning.</font>

519
00:29:09,748 --> 00:29:11,546
<font face="Serif" size="18">He is company-keeping,</font>

520
00:29:11,625 --> 00:29:14,003
<font face="Serif" size="18">and then the plan, it's...
it doesn't get planned.</font>

521
00:29:15,003 --> 00:29:16,425
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mm-hmm. Good one.
Shut up!</font>

522
00:29:16,505 --> 00:29:20,601
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay. So, maybe if you're not
planning later, we can hang out.</font>

523
00:29:20,676 --> 00:29:23,225
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sounds good.
Yes. You hear that?</font>

524
00:29:23,303 --> 00:29:25,055
<font face="Serif" size="18">It sounds good.</font>

525
00:29:25,180 --> 00:29:29,185
<font face="Serif" size="18">So you will hang out. See you
later, my honey. Lovely.</font>

526
00:29:29,851 --> 00:29:31,649
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, you're not hanging out.</font>

527
00:29:31,728 --> 00:29:33,651
<font face="Serif" size="18">Because you are leaving.</font>

528
00:29:33,730 --> 00:29:35,778
<font face="Serif" size="18">But the opposite, you said.</font>

529
00:29:39,278 --> 00:29:41,121
<font face="Serif" size="18">But, sir, the emergency.</font>

530
00:29:41,196 --> 00:29:42,743
<font face="Serif" size="18">Follow me.</font>

531
00:29:47,411 --> 00:29:49,379
<font face="Serif" size="18">Boy, that kid smelt.</font>

532
00:29:53,458 --> 00:29:54,835
<font face="Serif" size="18">Where are we going?</font>

533
00:29:54,918 --> 00:29:56,295
<font face="Serif" size="18">Just getting rid of you</font>

534
00:29:56,378 --> 00:29:59,131
<font face="Serif" size="18">through a secret tunnel
so she does not see us.</font>

535
00:29:59,298 --> 00:30:01,551
<font face="Serif" size="18">So, can I ask you a question?</font>

536
00:30:01,633 --> 00:30:03,977
<font face="Serif" size="18">Is that real, about
the garlic thing?</font>

