and Mom and kissing.</font>

890
00:51:26,834 --> 00:51:29,633
<font face="Serif" size="18">Dad, at some point,
I'm going to get married.</font>

891
00:51:29,712 --> 00:51:32,135
<font face="Serif" size="18">I can't be here forever.
What? Why not?</font>

892
00:51:32,214 --> 00:51:35,218
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're barely out of
your training fangs.</font>

893
00:52:07,458 --> 00:52:08,550
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ha-ha!</font>

894
00:52:08,626 --> 00:52:10,344
<font face="Serif" size="18">Quasi wins again!</font>

895
00:52:10,419 --> 00:52:14,094
<font face="Serif" size="18">When you bump with the hump,
you land on your rump!</font>

896
00:52:21,055 --> 00:52:23,183
<font face="Serif" size="18">But why all the
sudden interest?</font>

897
00:52:23,265 --> 00:52:26,018
<font face="Serif" size="18">Every time we used to talk
about love, it was always,</font>

898
00:52:26,101 --> 00:52:27,944
<font face="Serif" size="18">"Ooh, Dad, that's gross,"</font>

899
00:52:28,062 --> 00:52:30,781
<font face="Serif" size="18">and "Ooh, Dad, I don't want
to know about that."</font>

900
00:52:30,898 --> 00:52:32,150
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't know.</font>

901
00:52:33,067 --> 00:52:34,944
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sir, he made it into the kitchen.
He what?</font>

902
00:52:35,069 --> 00:52:36,412
<font face="Serif" size="18">What do I pay you for?</font>

903
00:52:36,487 --> 00:52:38,581
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm sorry, honey.
I have to go.</font>

904
00:52:40,574 --> 00:52:41,917
<font face="Serif" size="18">He doesn't pay me.</font>

905
00:52:46,121 --> 00:52:47,418
<font face="Serif" size="18">Before you kill me,</font>

906
00:52:47,498 --> 00:52:50,126
<font face="Serif" size="18">can I please talk to my
backpack one more time?</font>

907
00:52:50,209 --> 00:52:52,507
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't want to leave
anything unresolved.</font>

908
00:52:52,586 --> 00:52:54,805
<font face="Serif" size="18">Bonjour, Monsieur Dracula!</font>

909
00:52:54,880 --> 00:52:56,302
<font face="Serif" size="18">Shut your hump hole.</font>

910
00:52:56,382 --> 00:52:57,804
<font face="Serif" size="18">Now you are helping him?</font>

911
00:52:57,883 --> 00:52:59,931
<font face="Serif" size="18">What is it with you
and this human?</font>

912
00:53:00,010 --> 00:53:02,308
<font face="Serif" size="18">He is not human.
He's a Stein!</font>

913
00:53:02,388 --> 00:53:04,607
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's right, little man,
I'm a Stein!</font>

914
00:53:04,682 --> 00:53:08,607
<font face="Serif" size="18">If he is a monster,
let him scare Esmeralda!</font>

915
00:53:09,103 --> 00:53:10,229
<font face="Serif" size="18">The mouse?</font>

916
00:53:10,479 --> 00:53:12,356
<font face="Serif" size="18">Pfft! Without a doubt.</font>

917
00:53:12,898 --> 00:53:14,650
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay. Here we go.</font>

918
00:53:15,734 --> 00:53:17,111
<font face="Serif" size="18">Blargh!</font>

919
00:53:17,319 --> 00:53:18,821
<font face="Serif" size="18">Bleegh!</font>

920
00:53:18,904 --> 00:53:20,781
<font face="Serif" size="18">Blargy-bliggy-blargh!</font>

921
00:53:25,703 --> 00:53:28,923
<font face="Serif" size="18">A human! A human!</font>

922
00:53:28,997 --> 00:53:33,673
<font face="Serif" size="18">Monsieur Dracula has brought
a human into the...</font>

923
00:53:36,547 --> 00:53:40,142
<font face="Serif" size="18">Esmeralda, help me.</font>

924
00:53:52,271 --> 00:53:53,773
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, thanks for saving
me back there.</font>

925
00:53:53,856 --> 00:53:56,575
<font face="Serif" size="18">That guy's crazy!
Trying to eat me.</font>

926
00:53:56,650 --> 00:54:00,621
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's only happened to me one other time.
This weird dude at a Slipknot concert.</font>

927
00:54:00,696 --> 00:54:03,245
<font face="Serif" size="18">There's something
I need to show you.</font>

928
00:54:13,417 --> 00:54:14,885
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wow.</font>

929
00:54:14,960 --> 00:54:17,054
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, are we at
a funeral right now?</font>

930
00:54:17,129 --> 00:54:19,678
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, wait, no, it's your bed.</font>

931
00:54:20,632 --> 00:54:23,181
<font face="Serif" size="18">So creepy and cool.</font>

932
00:54:23,260 --> 00:54:25,228
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wow! I know her!</font>

933
00:54:25,304 --> 00:54:29,480
<font face="Serif" size="18">I've seen that picture at the ruins of Lubov.
That's my favorite castle.</font>

934
00:54:29,558 --> 00:54:31,481
<font face="Serif" size="18">There's a whole legend
around that lady.</font>

935
00:54:31,560 --> 00:54:32,652
<font face="Serif" size="18">A legend?</font>

936
00:54:34,396 --> 00:54:35,739
<font face="Serif" size="18">The Lady Lubov.</font>

937
00:54:36,774 --> 00:54:38,492
<font face="Serif" size="18">The story is that
a lonely count</font>

938
00:54:38,567 --> 00:54:41,662
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">met her by chance, and
they say that no two souls</font></font></i></font>

939
00:54:41,737 --> 00:54:43,831
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">were ever more meant
for each other.</font></font></i></font>

940
00:54:43,906 --> 00:54:47,752
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">Eventually, they settled down at
Castle Lubov and had a child.</font></font></i></font>

941
00:54:47,826 --> 00:54:51,456
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">But then, a horrible
tragedy happened.</font></font></i></font>

942
00:54:51,538 --> 00:54:56,089
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">A fire started mysteriously one
night, and it killed both of them.</font></font></i></font>

943
00:54:58,462 --> 00:55:03,434
<font face="Serif" size="18">When I was at the castle, I could
still feel their powerful love.</font>

944
00:55:03,509 --> 00:55:08,060
<font face="Serif" size="18">They say it's as if a soul is still
trapped in the ruins themselves.</font>

945
00:55:10,098 --> 00:55:11,520
<font face="Serif" size="18">The legend is wrong.</font>

946
00:55:12,851 --> 00:55:17,072
<font face="Serif" size="18">It was only the wife that died.</font>

947
00:55:24,029 --> 00:55:25,076
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh.</font>

948
00:55:25,781 --> 00:55:29,411
<font face="Serif" size="18">And it was no mystery
who killed her.</font>

949
00:55:30,619 --> 00:55:33,213
<font face="Serif" size="18">She was killed by your kind!</font>

950
00:55:34,248 --> 00:55:36,216
<font face="Serif" size="18">Vampire!</font>

951
00:55:37,167 --> 00:55:39,716
<font face="Serif" size="18">Honey? Go hide. I'll
take care of this.</font>

952
00:55:42,339 --> 00:55:43,636
<font face="Serif" size="18">Vampire!</font>

953
00:55:47,052 --> 00:55:48,929
<font face="Serif" size="18">Martha!</font>

954
00:55:50,472 --> 00:55:53,476
<font face="Serif" size="18">They are the real monsters.</font>

955
00:56:02,568 --> 00:56:07,199
<font face="Serif" size="18">I built this place for my
love, to protect her child.</font>

956
00:56:07,281 --> 00:56:11,206
<font face="Serif" size="18">As a father, you do everything
to keep your family safe,</font>

957
00:56:11,285 --> 00:56:15,040
<font face="Serif" size="18">even if you have
to break their trust.</font>

958
00:56:15,122 --> 00:56:19,753
<font face="Serif" size="18">But now, Mavis has
feelings for you.</font>

959
00:56:19,835 --> 00:56:20,927
<font face="Serif" size="18">What?</font>

960
00:56:21,003 --> 00:56:23,051
<font face="Serif" size="18">I just...</font>

961
00:56:25,215 --> 00:56:27,263
<font face="Serif" size="18">Awesome.
It's all right.</font>

962
00:56:27,342 --> 00:56:29,094
<font face="Serif" size="18">You are a good one.</font>

963
00:56:29,177 --> 00:56:31,851
<font face="Serif" size="18">If the world was different,
maybe it would be possible.</font>

964
00:56:32,514 --> 00:56:34,266
<font face="Serif" size="18">Drac, this is the 21st century.</font>

965
00:56:34,349 --> 00:56:36,477
<font face="Serif" size="18">People aren't the same
as they were back then.</font>

966
00:56:36,560 --> 00:56:39,939
<font face="Serif" size="18">Can you tell me for certain that
if we came out in the open,</font>

967
00:56:40,022 --> 00:56:41,444
<font face="Serif" size="18">everyone would accept us?</font>

968
00:56:41,523 --> 00:56:42,649
<font face="Serif" size="18">Everyone?</font>

969
00:56:46,153 --> 00:56:48,247
<font face="Serif" size="18">No. You're right.</font>

970
00:56:48,906 --> 00:56:50,908
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'll go for good this time.</font>

971
00:56:50,991 --> 00:56:53,289
<font face="Serif" size="18">You can just say
I had some emergency,</font>

972
00:56:53,368 --> 00:56:55,962
<font face="Serif" size="18">or the gremlin lady
ate me or something.</font>

973
00:56:56,038 --> 00:56:57,506
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, no, no, no, no.</font>

974
00:56:57,581 --> 00:57:00,380
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't want to ruin
her birthday party.</font>

975
00:57:00,459 --> 00:57:03,679
<font face="Serif" size="18">You can sneak out
after it's all done.</font>

976
00:57:03,754 --> 00:57:06,132
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm sorry.</font>

977
00:57:06,214 --> 00:57:09,559
<font face="Serif" size="18">The last thing I wanted
was to hurt her.</font>

978
00:57:09,635 --> 00:57:10,807
<font face="Serif" size="18">Or you.</font>

979
00:57:12,179 --> 00:57:15,774
<font face="Serif" size="18">You know, you're not
the smoothest Frankenstein,</font>

980
00:57:15,849 --> 00:57:18,352
<font face="Serif" size="18">but you'd make a great vampire.</font>

981
00:57:18,435 --> 00:57:19,527
<font face="Serif" size="18">For real?</font>

982
00:57:19,603 --> 00:57:21,355
<font face="Serif" size="18">'Cause I think I kind of got
your hypno-eyes down.</font>

983
00:57:21,438 --> 00:57:24,066
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, boy, here we go.
Let me see it.</font>

984
00:57:24,149 --> 00:57:27,528
<font face="Serif" size="18">Beware! For you
are in my power.</font>

985
00:57:27,611 --> 00:57:30,239
<font face="Serif" size="18">I command you to
be the werewolf man!</font>

986
00:57:32,449 --> 00:57:33,996
<font face="Serif" size="18">I have too many kids.</font>

987
00:57:35,953 --> 00:57:38,331
<font face="Serif" size="18">Someone scratch
me, I have fleas.</font>

988
00:57:39,915 --> 00:57:41,508
<font face="Serif" size="18">'Cause he's a wolf,
he'd get those.</font>

989
00:57:41,583 --> 00:57:43,130
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, no, don't explain it.</font>

990
00:57:43,210 --> 00:57:44,837
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's not funny
when you do that.</font>

991
00:58:06,316 --> 00:58:07,818
<font face="Serif" size="18">I didn't order
a wake-up call.</font>

992
00:58:07,901 --> 00:58:10,950
<font face="Serif" size="18">Count Dracula
arranged it for all the rooms.</font>

993
00:58:12,948 --> 00:58:14,245
<font face="Serif" size="18">Where's the snooze button?</font>

994
00:58:14,324 --> 00:58:16,543
<font face="Serif" size="18">There will be no snoozing.
The party's today.</font>

995
00:58:37,556 --> 00:58:40,605
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ooh, yeah, perfecto.</font>

996
00:59:20,682 --> 00:59:22,309
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wow.</font>

997
00:59:22,392 --> 00:59:24,611
<font face="Serif" size="18">You look beautiful.</font>

998
00:59:24,686 --> 00:59:26,939
<font face="Serif" size="18">Thanks. Thanks
for the party.</font>

999
00:59:27,022 --> 00:59:29,024
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, you like
my little touches?</font>

1000
00:59:51,588 --> 00:59:53,590
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's amazing.</font>

1001
01:00:02,015 --> 01:00:04,188
<font face="Serif" size="18">Terrific party. You really
outdid yourself, Drac.</font>

1002
01:00:04,267 --> 01:00:06,941
<font face="Serif" size="18">Got to be the best one
I've been to in 500 years.</font>

1003
01:00:16,905 --> 01:00:19,249
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sorry, big man.</font>

1004
01:00:39,511 --> 01:00:41,104
<font face="Serif" size="18">Uh, Mavis?</font>

1005
01:00:41,179 --> 01:00:43,056
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm crazily scared right now.</font>

1006
01:00:43,140 --> 01:00:45,518
<font face="Serif" size="18">Maybe that's a good thing.</font>

1007
01:00:57,696 --> 01:01:00,996
<font face="Serif" size="18">How could you? After I
shared my pain with you?</font>

1008
01:01:01,074 --> 01:01:02,747
<font face="Serif" size="18">But, no...
Dad, it was just a kiss.</font>

1009
01:01:02,826 --> 01:01:04,419
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, you're not allowed to kiss.</font>

1010
01:01:04,494 --> 01:01:07,919
<font face="Serif" size="18">Dad, I'm allowed to do things.
I'm not 83 any more.</font>

1011
01:01:07,998 --> 01:01:10,217
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm allowed to like people,
or go see the world again.</font>

1012
01:01:10,292 --> 01:01:12,920
<font face="Serif" size="18">What? You saw it! You
said you didn't like it!</font>

1013
01:01:13,003 --> 01:01:14,883
<font face="Serif" size="18">Maybe I want to give
the village another chance.</font>

1014
01:01:14,921 --> 01:01:17,925
<font face="Serif" size="18">I just need to learn, you know, just
how to roll with it, like Johnny does.</font>

1015
01:01:18,008 --> 01:01:20,932
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, no, you can't go
to the village again.</font>

1016
01:01:21,011 --> 01:01:22,479
<font face="Serif" size="18">Maybe you can make them see
that we could be friends.</font>

1017
01:01:22,554 --> 01:01:24,056
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, that isn't possible.</font>

1018
01:01:24,139 --> 01:01:26,358
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, you can't be sure. It's all
in how you present yourself.</font>

1019
01:01:26,433 --> 01:01:28,310
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, that won't make a difference!
How do you know?</font>

1020
01:01:28,393 --> 01:01:29,736
<font face="Serif" size="18">Because it just won't!
Why? Why won't it?</font>

1021
01:01:29,811 --> 01:01:32,314
<font face="Serif" size="18">Because that village
doesn't really exist!</font>

1022
01:01:37,152 --> 01:01:39,905
<font face="Serif" size="18">What do you mean
"doesn't exist"?</font>

1023
01:01:39,988 --> 01:01:41,831
<font face="Serif" size="18">What did you do?</font>

1024
01:01:41,907 --> 01:01:44,251
<font face="Serif" size="18">I did what I had to do.</font>

1025
01:01:44,326 --> 01:01:45,452
<font face="Serif" size="18">What was it?</font>

1026
01:01:45,535 --> 01:01:49,165
<font face="Serif" size="18">What exactly did you
have to do? Tell me!</font>

1027
01:01:50,832 --> 01:01:56,305
<font face="Serif" size="18">I... I built the town. The
staff put it all together.</font>

1028
01:01:56,379 --> 01:02:00,509
<font face="Serif" size="18">The zombies dressed up
as the townspeople.</font>

1029
01:02:02,385 --> 01:02:04,479
<font face="Serif" size="18">Please. I...</font>

1030
01:02:04,554 --> 01:02:07,808
<font face="Serif" size="18">If you really went out there
and something happened to you,</font>

1031
01:02:07,891 --> 01:02:10,485
<font face="Serif" size="18">I just couldn't
live with myself.</font>

1032
01:02:10,560 --> 01:02:14,736
<font face="Serif" size="18">But you can live with this?
Lying to me? Tricking me?</font>

1033
01:02:14,814 --> 01:02:17,988
<font face="Serif" size="18">Keeping me here forever when
you knew my dream was to go.</font>

1034
01:02:19,277 --> 01:02:21,700
<font face="Serif" size="18">Liar! Liar!</font>

1035
01:02:22,489 --> 01:02:23,741
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oil?</font>

1036
01:02:23,823 --> 01:02:25,746
<font face="Serif" size="18">Uh-uh-uh!</font>

1037
01:02:27,202 --> 01:02:28,749
<font face="Serif" size="18">English, please.</font>

1038
01:02:28,828 --> 01:02:30,876
<font face="Serif" size="18">Your voice is really annoying.</font>

1039
01:02:30,956 --> 01:02:32,503
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait, I speak frozen.</font>

1040
01:02:32,582 --> 01:02:36,086
<font face="Serif" size="18">He says, "Dracula has brought
a human into the hotel."</font>

1041
01:02:37,629 --> 01:02:39,677
<font face="Serif" size="18">A human?
Stay close, pookie!</font>

1042
01:02:42,259 --> 01:02:44,432
<font face="Serif" size="18">He says,
"There is ze human."</font>

1043
01:02:44,511 --> 01:02:46,058
<font face="Serif" size="18">He has a French accent.</font>

1044
01:02:51,518 --> 01:02:54,271
<font face="Serif" size="18">Johnny's not a human.
He's my right arm's cousin.</font>

1045
01:02:54,354 --> 01:02:56,448
<font face="Serif" size="18">- He's lying.
- Yeah.</font>

1046
01:02:56,523 --> 01:02:57,775
<font face="Serif" size="18">And why is he picking his nose?</font>

1047
01:02:59,484 --> 01:03:01,862
<font face="Serif" size="18">He says, "it's a long story."</font>

1048
01:03:01,945 --> 01:03:04,289
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, wait, no! Get off me!</font>

1049
01:03:04,364 --> 01:03:05,411
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ew!</font>

1050
01:03:07,659 --> 01:03:10,287
<font face="Serif" size="18">He says, "Behold ze human."</font>

1051
01:03:12,789 --> 01:03:14,291
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't believe it.</font>

1052
01:03:20,714 --> 01:03:23,809
<font face="Serif" size="18">Is it true?
Are you a human?</font>

1053
01:03:24,467 --> 01:03:26,970
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yes.</font>

1054
01:03:27,595 --> 01:03:29,438
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm so sorry.</font>

1055
01:03:31,141 --> 01:03:34,190
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't care. I still
want to be with you.</font>

1056
01:03:42,444 --> 01:03:43,491
<font face="Serif" size="18">Uh...</font>

1057
01:03:43,987 --> 01:03:48,333
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, tough. 'Cause I don't
want to be with you.</font>

1058
01:03:48,408 --> 01:03:51,912
<font face="Serif" size="18">Because you're a monster.
And I hate monsters.</font>

1059
01:03:53,830 --> 01:03:55,548
<font face="Serif" size="18">Goodbye.</font>

1060
01:03:56,541 --> 01:03:58,543
<font face="Serif" size="18">Please don't hurt me!</font>

1061
01:04:02,047 --> 01:04:04,141
<font face="Serif" size="18">This is all your fault!</font>

1062
01:04:06,051 --> 01:04:08,804
<font face="Serif" size="18">We're getting out of here.
I'm never coming back here.</font>

1063
01:04:08,887 --> 01:04:12,733
<font face="Serif" size="18">I thought I smelt a human.
"Human-free"? What a rip.</font>

1064
01:04:24,694 --> 01:04:27,197
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh. Here he comes.
Count Crock-ula.</font>

1065
01:04:27,280 --> 01:04:31,581
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm just glad my eyes are stitched
shut, 'cause I don't even want to...</font>

1066
01:04:33,870 --> 01:04:36,794
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mavis, honey, are you in there?</font>

1067
01:04:38,875 --> 01:04:41,594
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mavis? Mavis?</font>

1068
01:04:42,420 --> 01:04:45,594
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mavis, where are you?</font>

1069
01:04:45,673 --> 01:04:47,516
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mavis?</font>

1070
01:05:07,070 --> 01:05:10,165
<font face="Serif" size="18">Dad, can you do me a favor?</font>

1071
01:05:10,240 --> 01:05:13,665
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yes, yes, of course,
darling. Anything.</font>

1072
01:05:13,743 --> 01:05:15,461
<font face="Serif" size="18">Will you erase my mind?</font>

1073
01:05:17,872 --> 01:05:20,967
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, no, no, no.
No, I won't do that.</font>

1074
01:05:21,042 --> 01:05:23,921
<font face="Serif" size="18">There's too much
I want you to remember.</font>

1075
01:05:24,003 --> 01:05:27,758
<font face="Serif" size="18">You were right, Dad.
The humans hate us.</font>

1076
01:05:27,841 --> 01:05:31,641
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sweetheart, there are so many
eligible monsters out there.</font>

1077
01:05:31,719 --> 01:05:33,062
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're so young to...</font>

1078
01:05:34,347 --> 01:05:36,645
<font face="Serif" size="18">What is it? What
are you reading?</font>

1079
01:05:43,940 --> 01:05:46,443
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">"Two lonely bats
crashed in the night."</font></font></i></font>

1080
01:05:48,153 --> 01:05:52,579
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">"They felt a Zing.
Love at first sight."</font></font></i></font>

1081
01:05:53,032 --> 01:05:57,037
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">"They knew right then they
would be husband and wife."</font></font></i></font>

1082
01:05:57,787 --> 01:06:02,293
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">"For a Zing only happens
once in your life."</font></font></i></font>

1083
01:06:02,834 --> 01:06:05,007
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">"Your Zing will come, my love."</font></font></i></font>

1084
01:06:05,086 --> 01:06:06,508
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">"Cherish it."</font></font></i></font>

1085
01:06:06,588 --> 01:06:09,011
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">"Love, Mommy."</font></font></i></font>

1086
01:06:12,594 --> 01:06:16,690
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I thought we Zinged, Dad.
- You and Johnny?</font>

1087
01:06:16,764 --> 01:06:19,483
<font face="Serif" size="18">I guess it was only me.</font>

1088
01:06:19,559 --> 01:06:21,607
<font face="Serif" size="18">But you should be happy, Dad.</font>

1089
01:06:21,686 --> 01:06:23,609
<font face="Serif" size="18">There's no reason
for me to leave.</font>

1090
01:06:23,688 --> 01:06:28,159
<font face="Serif" size="18">I have no more dreams.
I'm just like you now.</font>

1091
01:06:54,469 --> 01:06:57,598
<font face="Serif" size="18">Martha, what have I done?</font>

1092
01:07:04,145 --> 01:07:05,772
<font face="Serif" size="18">Where is my bill?
Over here. I'm next.</font>

1093
01:07:05,897 --> 01:07:08,867
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm checking out. Take my key!
Take my key!</font>

1094
01:07:10,151 --> 01:07:11,323
<font face="Serif" size="18">What is this minibar charge?</font>

1095
01:07:11,402 --> 01:07:13,530
<font face="Serif" size="18">Honey, the kids threw
the minibar out the window.</font>

1096
01:07:13,613 --> 01:07:15,707
<font face="Serif" size="18">And that's our fault?
Well...</font>

1097
01:07:15,782 --> 01:07:18,376
<font face="Serif" size="18">Excuse me!
Pardon, yeah.</font>

1098
01:07:18,451 --> 01:07:21,830
<font face="Serif" size="18">Excuse me, I got a couple
of people to express mail.</font>

1099
01:07:23,248 --> 01:07:25,125
<font face="Serif" size="18">Friends, please, stop.</font>

1100
01:07:25,208 --> 01:07:27,336
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's too late, rat-bat!</font>

1101
01:07:27,418 --> 01:07:28,886
<font face="Serif" size="18">Please, I'm begging you.</font>

1102
01:07:28,962 --> 01:07:31,715
<font face="Serif" size="18">I need you to help
me find Johnny.</font>

1103
01:07:31,798 --> 01:07:33,846
<font face="Serif" size="18">The human? He
could've killed us!</font>

1104
01:07:33,925 --> 01:07:35,723
<font face="Serif" size="18">He touched my guitar!</font>

1105
01:07:35,802 --> 01:07:39,978
<font face="Serif" size="18">He put his hand in my mouth
to see if it would disappear.</font>

1106
01:07:40,056 --> 01:07:43,526
<font face="Serif" size="18">He let me eat his scooter!</font>

1107
01:07:44,936 --> 01:07:47,280
<font face="Serif" size="18">I know I lied.</font>

1108
01:07:47,355 --> 01:07:48,948
<font face="Serif" size="18">I was wrong.</font>

1109
01:07:49,023 --> 01:07:50,946
<font face="Serif" size="18">But you have to believe this:</font>

1110
01:07:51,025 --> 01:07:54,700
<font face="Serif" size="18">Johnny wasn't a bad guy.</font>

1111
01:07:55,697 --> 01:07:59,952
<font face="Serif" size="18">The truth is, I don't even know
if humans are bad any more.</font>

1112
01:08:02,787 --> 01:08:06,337
<font face="Serif" size="18">Frank, come on, buddy.
You understand.</font>

1113
01:08:06,416 --> 01:08:07,918
<font face="Serif" size="18">He's not talking to you.</font>

1114
01:08:08,001 --> 01:08:10,379
<font face="Serif" size="18">First you tell us humans
are bad, now they're good.</font>

1115
01:08:10,461 --> 01:08:13,465
<font face="Serif" size="18">What else? Up is down, cold
is hot, gremlins don't smell.</font>

1116
01:08:13,548 --> 01:08:15,550
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey!</font>

1117
01:08:16,926 --> 01:08:21,181
<font face="Serif" size="18">I really liked Johnny, cousin or no.
He told fun stories.</font>

1118
01:08:21,264 --> 01:08:23,312
<font face="Serif" size="18">I think they Zinged.</font>

1119
01:08:23,391 --> 01:08:24,688
<font face="Serif" size="18">They Zinged?</font>

1120
01:08:24,767 --> 01:08:26,940
<font face="Serif" size="18">But I got in the way.</font>

1121
01:08:27,604 --> 01:08:30,483
<font face="Serif" size="18">You only Zing
once in your life.</font>

1122
01:08:31,357 --> 01:08:34,486
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oy, now you're short-circuiting.
I don't care!</font>

1123
01:08:34,569 --> 01:08:37,288
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, what are we doing?
Let's get Johnny. Come on!</font>

1124
01:08:37,363 --> 01:08:39,582
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, let's do it!
Come on!</font>

1125
01:08:43,036 --> 01:08:44,208
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah!</font>

1126
01:08:45,330 --> 01:08:48,504
<font face="Serif" size="18">We should have
honeymooned at your parents!</font>

1127
01:09:00,303 --> 01:09:01,805
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, okay, where am I going?</font>

1128
01:09:01,888 --> 01:09:04,983
<font face="Serif" size="18">The human world, before
Johnny's gone forever.</font>

1129
01:09:05,058 --> 01:09:06,184
<font face="Serif" size="18">But what about the sun?</font>

1130
01:09:06,809 --> 01:09:10,279
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't know. I'll
just have to roll.</font>

1131
01:09:10,355 --> 01:09:12,232
<font face="Serif" size="18">He just rolls.
Rollability.</font>

1132
01:09:13,149 --> 01:09:14,629
<font face="Serif" size="18">So we follow
his boot-prints.</font>

1133
01:09:14,651 --> 01:09:17,074
<font face="Serif" size="18">When they run out, that's
where you come in, Wayne.</font>

1134
01:09:17,153 --> 01:09:18,325
<font face="Serif" size="18">Me?
There!</font>

1135
01:09:20,948 --> 01:09:24,418
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yes, I knew something would
fall out of that backpack.</font>

1136
01:09:25,703 --> 01:09:28,047
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yowch! That stinks!</font>

1137
01:09:28,122 --> 01:09:29,374
<font face="Serif" size="18">Work your magic.</font>

1138
01:09:29,457 --> 01:09:31,551
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait, you want me
to track the smell?</font>

1139
01:09:31,626 --> 01:09:33,970
<font face="Serif" size="18">No. My sniffing tracking
days are way behind me.</font>

1140
01:09:34,087 --> 01:09:35,964
<font face="Serif" size="18">Do you know how many
diapers I've changed?</font>

1141
01:09:36,047 --> 01:09:38,641
<font face="Serif" size="18">How many number twos
have destroyed this thing?</font>

1142
01:09:38,716 --> 01:09:40,263
<font face="Serif" size="18">But...</font>

1143
01:09:53,648 --> 01:09:55,867
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey! Take it easy!
Watch it!</font>

1144
01:09:56,901 --> 01:09:58,403
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sit.</font>

1145
01:09:59,278 --> 01:10:01,531
<font face="Serif" size="18">Smell. I said smell.</font>

1146
01:10:03,908 --> 01:10:06,627
<font face="Serif" size="18">Not me, the shirt!
The shirt!</font>

1147
01:10:06,703 --> 01:10:09,456
<font face="Serif" size="18">Do any of your kids
still respect you?</font>

1148
01:10:09,539 --> 01:10:12,258
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mm, give me
a second. Oh, yeah.</font>

1149
01:10:12,333 --> 01:10:15,428
<font face="Serif" size="18">Winnie! Front and center!</font>

1150
01:10:24,637 --> 01:10:27,891
<font face="Serif" size="18">He got into a car.
A '86 Fiat.</font>

1151
01:10:27,974 --> 01:10:32,229
<font face="Serif" size="18">It needs a little transmission
work, but otherwise okay.</font>

1152
01:10:32,311 --> 01:10:37,408
<font face="Serif" size="18">It drove through town to the airport.
Flight 497.</font>

1153
01:10:37,483 --> 01:10:38,951
<font face="Serif" size="18">8:00 a.m. departure.</font>

1154
01:10:39,026 --> 01:10:40,869
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's in 15 minutes.</font>

1155
01:10:40,945 --> 01:10:42,572
<font face="Serif" size="18">Seat 23A.</font>

1156
01:10:43,197 --> 01:10:44,824
<font face="Serif" size="18">He ordered the vegetarian meal.</font>

1157
01:10:44,907 --> 01:10:47,285
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, thank you, cutie.</font>

1158
01:10:47,410 --> 01:10:49,458
<font face="Serif" size="18">Now, all of you,
go back to your mother!</font>

1159
01:10:57,920 --> 01:10:59,046
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sheep!</font>

1160
01:11:08,681 --> 01:11:11,560
<font face="Serif" size="18">High five! Don't
leave me hanging.</font>

1161
01:11:12,685 --> 01:11:14,687
<font face="Serif" size="18">Lots of sheep!
I got this one.</font>

1162
01:11:21,819 --> 01:11:24,914
<font face="Serif" size="18">What? Now there's no sheep in the road.
Let's go.</font>

1163
01:11:24,989 --> 01:11:26,582
<font face="Serif" size="18">That was pretty sick, man.</font>

1164
01:11:26,657 --> 01:11:29,035
<font face="Serif" size="18">You eat lamb chops,
it's the same thing.</font>

1165
01:11:29,118 --> 01:11:31,158
<font face="Serif" size="18">We don't have time for this.
Come on, let's move it!</font>

1166
01:11:35,333 --> 01:11:37,210
<font face="Serif" size="18">Look, a human.</font>

1167
01:11:38,878 --> 01:11:43,634
<font face="Serif" size="18">Welcome to Transylvania!</font>

1168
01:11:46,219 --> 01:11:48,768
<font face="Serif" size="18">That was trippy.</font>

1169
01:11:48,888 --> 01:11:50,435
<font face="Serif" size="18">Monster Festival?</font>

1170
01:11:51,182 --> 01:11:52,399
<font face="Serif" size="18">What's a Monster Festival?</font>

1171
01:11:59,065 --> 01:12:01,318
<font face="Serif" size="18">Did they know we were coming?</font>

1172
01:12:24,298 --> 01:12:25,891
<font face="Serif" size="18">They like us?</font>

1173
01:12:25,967 --> 01:12:27,469
<font face="Serif" size="18">Really?</font>

1174
01:12:28,886 --> 01:12:31,435
<font face="Serif" size="18">Excuse me? Do you know the
best way to the airport?</font>

1175
01:12:31,556 --> 01:12:35,311
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yes, fellow Dracula. There's only one way.
Bleh, bleh-bleh.</font>

1176
01:12:36,102 --> 01:12:39,026
<font face="Serif" size="18">But it's all blocked.
We'll never make it in time.</font>

1177
01:12:39,105 --> 01:12:41,858
<font face="Serif" size="18">You should have left an hour earlier.
Bleh, bleh-bleh.</font>

1178
01:12:41,941 --> 01:12:44,615
<font face="Serif" size="18">I do not say
"Bleh, bleh-bleh."</font>

1179
01:12:45,236 --> 01:12:48,080
<font face="Serif" size="18">All right, let's just run
through it on foot.</font>

1180
01:12:53,995 --> 01:12:56,123
<font face="Serif" size="18">Drac, this'll protect you.</font>

1181
01:12:56,330 --> 01:12:57,627
<font face="Serif" size="18">Bleh, bleh-bleh.</font>

1182
01:12:57,748 --> 01:13:00,467
<font face="Serif" size="18">Imagine if that guy knew he
was talking to the real Drac.</font>

1183
01:13:00,585 --> 01:13:02,258
<font face="Serif" size="18">He'd run for the hills!</font>

1184
01:13:02,336 --> 01:13:04,589
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hold it, now. Hold it, now.</font>

1185
01:13:04,672 --> 01:13:06,219
<font face="Serif" size="18">That sounds spot on.</font>

1186
01:13:06,299 --> 01:13:10,475
<font face="Serif" size="18">But the only way they'd know the
real us is if we show the real us.</font>

1187
01:13:10,595 --> 01:13:11,767
<font face="Serif" size="18">This could work.</font>

1188
01:13:11,846 --> 01:13:14,565
<font face="Serif" size="18">You mean, like, scare them? We
haven't scared people in centuries.</font>

1189
01:13:14,640 --> 01:13:16,893
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't even think
I have it in me any more.</font>

1190
01:13:20,021 --> 01:13:21,614
<font face="Serif" size="18">I got nothing.
I really got nothing.</font>

1191
01:13:21,689 --> 01:13:23,316
<font face="Serif" size="18">Let's just move this along.</font>

1192
01:13:29,655 --> 01:13:32,875
<font face="Serif" size="18">Fire! Fire!</font>

1193
01:13:32,992 --> 01:13:34,335
<font face="Serif" size="18">Fire!</font>

1194
01:13:47,798 --> 01:13:50,551
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm trying to scare you!</font>

1195
01:13:50,676 --> 01:13:52,394
<font face="Serif" size="18">The real Frankenstein!</font>

1196
01:13:52,511 --> 01:13:54,479
<font face="Serif" size="18">We know! We love you!</font>

1197
01:13:54,555 --> 01:13:56,023
<font face="Serif" size="18">Can you sign my torch?</font>

1198
01:13:57,642 --> 01:14:03,615
<font face="Serif" size="18">Listen, before anything else,
down there's the real Dracula!</font>

1199
01:14:03,689 --> 01:14:05,191
<font face="Serif" size="18">Prove it.</font>

1200
01:14:06,192 --> 01:14:07,489
<font face="Serif" size="18">All right. Continue.</font>

1201
01:14:07,568 --> 01:14:11,414
<font face="Serif" size="18">Drac's daughter's in love, and
he's got to get to the airport!</font>

1202
01:14:11,530 --> 01:14:13,703
<font face="Serif" size="18">And he can't get
through this crowd!</font>

1203
01:14:13,824 --> 01:14:17,374
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why doesn't he fly? The sun, you idiot.
He's a vampire.</font>

1204
01:14:17,495 --> 01:14:20,123
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's right. Thank you,
Monster Nerd.</font>

1205
01:14:20,206 --> 01:14:25,087
<font face="Serif" size="18">So, people, if you really are our
friends, clear a path for the man!</font>

1206
01:14:25,211 --> 01:14:29,216
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay. All Draculas,
line up. Bleh, bleh-bleh.</font>

1207
01:14:32,885 --> 01:14:37,356
<font face="Serif" size="18">Everyone else, lift the capes.
Protect our friend. Bleh, bleh-bleh.</font>

1208
01:14:45,356 --> 01:14:47,233
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's all for you, buddy.</font>

1209
01:14:48,526 --> 01:14:50,153
<font face="Serif" size="18">Go ahead.</font>

1210
01:14:50,236 --> 01:14:51,488
<font face="Serif" size="18">Good luck!
Go get 'em!</font>

1211
01:14:51,570 --> 01:14:52,617
<font face="Serif" size="18">Go, Drac, go!</font>

1212
01:14:52,738 --> 01:14:54,581
<font face="Serif" size="18">Go, Drac!
Go, Drac!</font>

1213
01:14:54,657 --> 01:14:56,204
<font face="Serif" size="18">Go, Drac!</font>

1214
01:14:58,244 --> 01:15:00,042
<font face="Serif" size="18">Go, Drac!</font>

1215
01:15:02,540 --> 01:15:04,338
<font face="Serif" size="18">Go, Drac!</font>

1216
01:15:04,417 --> 01:15:06,135
<font face="Serif" size="18">Go get 'em!</font>

1217
01:15:06,585 --> 01:15:09,338
<font face="Serif" size="18">Go, Drac, go!</font>

1218
01:15:09,422 --> 01:15:12,801
<font face="Serif" size="18">We love you, Dracula!</font>

1219
01:15:27,523 --> 01:15:28,820
<font face="Serif" size="18">There's no choice.</font>

1220
01:16:07,021 --> 01:16:08,648
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ouch. Ouch, ouch, ouch.</font>

1221
01:16:08,731 --> 01:16:10,825
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay. Okay, I must do this.</font>

1222
01:16:29,126 --> 01:16:32,676
<font face="Serif" size="18">Jonathan. Jonathan,
can you hear me?</font>

1223
01:16:32,755 --> 01:16:35,804
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">Tell me, do you dream
of being a vampire?</font></font></i></font>

1224
01:16:35,883 --> 01:16:38,932
<font face="Serif" size="18">This is how we're represented.
Unbelievable.</font>

1225
01:16:39,011 --> 01:16:41,105
<font face="Serif" size="18">Jonathan. Jonathan.</font>

1226
01:16:41,806 --> 01:16:43,103
<font face="Serif" size="18">Can you hear me?</font>

1227
01:16:43,182 --> 01:16:44,684
<font face="Serif" size="18">Whoa! Bat!</font>

1228
01:16:44,767 --> 01:16:47,611
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait, it's talking.
Dracula? Is that you?</font>

1229
01:16:49,230 --> 01:16:50,402
<font face="Serif" size="18">Huh? Dracula.</font>

1230
01:16:50,481 --> 01:16:53,030
<font face="Serif" size="18">I can't understand you.</font>

1231
01:16:53,109 --> 01:16:56,113
<font face="Serif" size="18">What? My hand's
in a tan shoe?</font>

1232
01:16:56,195 --> 01:17:00,291
<font face="Serif" size="18">What? Japan's
eating lamb stew?</font>

1233
01:17:00,366 --> 01:17:02,368
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, do you know
you're smoking?</font>

1234
01:17:08,207 --> 01:17:09,299
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh.</font>

1235
01:17:09,375 --> 01:17:10,627
<font face="Serif" size="18">Pardon me. Sorry, excuse me.</font>

1236
01:17:10,709 --> 01:17:12,382
<font face="Serif" size="18">Whoa! Excuse me.</font>

1237
01:17:26,851 --> 01:17:29,229
<font face="Serif" size="18">What the heck? How'd a
bat get up this high?</font>

1238
01:17:30,020 --> 01:17:34,196
<font face="Serif" size="18">Folks, I'm gonna turn on the seat belt sign.
Just a precaution while we...</font>

1239
01:17:36,652 --> 01:17:41,624
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">While we hear a special announcement
for my dear friend Jonathan.</font></font></i></font>

1240
01:17:41,699 --> 01:17:42,871
<font face="Serif" size="18">Dracula?</font>

1241
01:17:42,950 --> 01:17:47,330
<font face="Serif" size="18">My dear boy, I have
made a terrible mistake.</font>

1242
01:17:47,413 --> 01:17:51,043
<font face="Serif" size="18">I was trying to keep
my baby to myself,</font>

1243
01:17:51,125 --> 01:17:53,799
<font face="Serif" size="18">because I knew I would
always protect her.</font>

1244
01:17:53,878 --> 01:17:59,476
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">But I realize now, children need
to discover things for themselves.</font></font></i></font>

1245
01:17:59,550 --> 01:18:03,475
<font face="Serif" size="18">They'll stumble and fall,
laugh and cry,</font>

1246
01:18:03,554 --> 01:18:05,352
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">but such is life.</font></font></i></font>

1247
01:18:05,431 --> 01:18:08,810
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">The truth is, you and
Mavis are meant to be.</font></font></i></font>

1248
01:18:08,893 --> 01:18:10,361
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">You Zinged.</font></font></i></font>

1249
01:18:10,436 --> 01:18:13,360
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">If she must give her
trust to someone else,</font></font></i></font>

1250
01:18:13,439 --> 01:18:16,534
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">I'm thankful that it
is you, Jonathan.</font></font></i></font>

1251
01:18:16,609 --> 01:18:20,955
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">I hope you can hear me</font></font></i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">
<i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">and forgive me-</font></font></i></font>

1252
01:18:34,793 --> 01:18:39,424
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">Okay, folks, we're going to make
a quick turnaround to refuel,</font></font></i></font>

1253
01:18:39,506 --> 01:18:41,725
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">and then we'll be
back on our way.</font></font></i></font>

1254
01:18:42,843 --> 01:18:45,687
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i><font size="18"><font face="Serif">Quit your whining!
I'm burning up out here!</font></font></i></font>

1255
01:18:59,068 --> 01:19:00,160
<font face="Serif" size="18">Dad?</font>

1256
01:19:01,904 --> 01:19:06,455
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm fine. I'm just
a little sunburnt.</font>

1257
01:19:08,911 --> 01:19:10,083
<font face="Serif" size="18">Honey,</font>

1258
01:19:11,664 --> 01:19:15,760
<font face="Serif" size="18">I always thought the worst thing
ever would be seeing you go.</font>

1259
01:19:15,834 --> 01:19:19,338
<font face="Serif" size="18">But the worst is
seeing you unhappy.</font>

1260
01:19:19,421 --> 01:19:22,470
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mavey, I want you
to live your life.</font>

1261
01:19:24,677 --> 01:19:26,771
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't know how
I'm supposed to do that.</font>

1262
01:19:28,430 --> 01:19:31,730
<font face="Serif" size="18">You know, Mommy already
gave you her birthday present.</font>

1263
01:19:31,809 --> 01:19:33,811
<font face="Serif" size="18">Can I now give you mine?</font>

1264
01:19:36,438 --> 01:19:37,690
<font face="Serif" size="18">What do I need this for?</font>

1265
01:19:37,773 --> 01:19:40,242
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, it comes with an accessory.</font>

1266
01:19:42,152 --> 01:19:44,655
<font face="Serif" size="18">You?
You.</font>

1267
01:19:45,406 --> 01:19:46,828
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why are you back?</font>

1268
01:19:50,744 --> 01:19:52,667
<font face="Serif" size="18">'Cause you're my Zing, Mavis.</font>

1269
01:19:52,788 --> 01:19:54,756
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm your Zing?</font>

1270
01:19:54,832 --> 01:19:57,676
<font face="Serif" size="18">But you told me
you hate monsters.</font>

1271
01:19:57,751 --> 01:20:00,675
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, well, I was afraid
your dad was gonna</font>

1272
01:20:00,754 --> 01:20:03,052
<font face="Serif" size="18">suck all the blood out of my
body if I didn't say that.</font>

1273
01:20:03,132 --> 01:20:04,850
<font face="Serif" size="18">I wouldn't have...</font>

1274
01:20:04,925 --> 01:20:06,802
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, he's right,
I would have done that.</font>

1275
01:20:06,885 --> 01:20:09,934
<font face="Serif" size="18">Dad.
I was wrong, Devil-chops.</font>

1276
01:20:13,559 --> 01:20:15,653
<font face="Serif" size="18">Do you really mean it, Dad?</font>

1277
01:20:17,104 --> 01:20:19,357
<font face="Serif" size="18">Go make your own paradise.</font>

1278
01:20:22,985 --> 01:20:25,488
<font face="Serif" size="18">Can we try that
kiss over again?</font>

1279
01:20:25,571 --> 01:20:28,199
<font face="Serif" size="18">I think we can.</font>

1280
01:20:32,244 --> 01:20:35,874
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sorry. I just...
I got to get used to that.</font>

1281
01:20:35,956 --> 01:20:38,584
<font face="Serif" size="18">Go. Do your thing.</font>

1282
01:20:48,969 --> 01:20:50,516
<font face="Serif" size="18">Stop! Stop!</font>

1283
01:21:32,346 --> 01:21:34,144
<font face="Serif" size="18">Drac, you ready to throw down?</font>

1284
01:21:34,223 --> 01:21:37,397
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, no, I just came closer
to hear you better.</font>

1285
01:21:37,476 --> 01:21:39,353
<font face="Serif" size="18">Come on, just give it a try.</font>

1286
01:21:39,478 --> 01:21:41,446
<font face="Serif" size="18">All right, maybe just a little.</font>

1287
01:22:48,005 --> 01:22:50,007
<font face="Serif" size="18">Housekeeping!</font>

1288
01:25:46,683 --> 01:31:31,520
<font face="Serif" size="18">I didn't do that.</font>